Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.91,0:03:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原地趴下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.87,0:03:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}并不冷？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里12月是夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}碰上温暖的日子 有时白天温度不会降到冰点以下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的不冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.54,0:03:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在行李送到 忙起来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我带你们快速参观一下基地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里就是昭和基地…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.43,0:03:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个像是立方体堆成的建筑是管理楼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用家打比方的话 就是所有人会聚一起的客厅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.76,0:03:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是发电楼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:03:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这些是居住楼和仓库
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是湖滨旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.98,0:04:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}湖滨？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们帮夏季队的宿舍取的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过冬的队员 一般会住在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过三年没来了 那边短时间也整顿不完
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再考虑到你们是女生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以你们各自有单人房
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里的家具都可以用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里的空气很干燥 准备好迎接静电吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.21,0:04:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过地板有供暖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且拉开百叶窗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}终于不用担心小理成天说梦话了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我那么会说梦话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}超会的 你总是眼睛一睁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.69,0:04:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}壶魔人不肯出厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肯定通不过检票了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么壶魔人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:04:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下来本来要去管理楼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但行李也快要送过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.23,0:05:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们回直升机停机坪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.67,0:05:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个肯定得换一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来打扫一番啰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下一波送到前休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还撑得住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没问题 我有在搬家公司打过工
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那休息10分钟 就帮我去那边装货
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我收到封简讯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}刚刚我们在基地里的时候 可能就发到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.09,0:05:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}管理楼附近能收到电波讯号的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在南极也能用手机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是企鹅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:06:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别叫那么大声
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小结 准备拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}保持五公尺外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:08.56,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}企…鹅！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.40,0:06:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我开拍了 小结准备开始报导
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:13.47,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}往我们这边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来了 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}停停停停 笨蛋 保持五公尺距离
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}站住站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真会闹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.47,0:06:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以把脏雪倒进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说是等会要过滤的 可以倒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.97,0:07:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你脱掉会晒伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.77,0:07:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都喘不上气了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}话说 要做的事真是一个接一个的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三年没人来过这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这阵子大概都得这么忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不想做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有忙碌才是最能推动表针前进的事！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又是你随口说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.60,0:07:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是我在便利商店打工时想的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我大概是喜欢忙忙碌碌的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.98,0:07:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好累
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也不讨厌忙忙碌碌的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这段旅途是我们一起走过来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一起聊了很多 也玩了很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.44,0:07:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你突然问些什么东西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}电视剧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.34,0:07:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}出发前我参加了试镜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}招的是晨间剧里 主角的挚友角色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不会吧 你被选中了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
