Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.99,0:08:06.39,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康中特圆体\bord0\b0\fs25\1c&H6D7179&\frz10.05\frx324\fry2\pos(508,92)}漂亮！中了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.99,0:08:06.39,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康中特圆体\bord0\b0\fs25\1c&H6D7179&\frx336\fry0\frz9.463\pos(710,146)}晨间剧试镜通过了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.99,0:08:06.39,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康中特圆体\bord0\b0\fs25\1c&H6D7179&\frx336\fry0\frz9.463\pos(730,192)}恭喜你！你真棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.99,0:08:06.39,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康中特圆体\bord0\b0\fs25\1c&H6D7179&\frx336\fry0\frz9.463\pos(622,280)}记得照顾好自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.99,0:08:06.39,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康中特圆体\bord0\b0\fs25\1c&H6D7179&\frx336\fry0\frz9.463\pos(634,324)}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.99,0:08:06.39,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康中特圆体\bord0\b0\fs25\1c&H6D7179&\frx336\fry0\frz9.463\pos(648,370)}本讯息来自myPhone
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好归好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.29,0:08:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是要拍电视剧就会没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不能像这样和你们在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不想要这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但就算没有电视剧 我们也是各过各的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.53,0:08:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没关系 大家都是挚友了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}挚友…我们是挚友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别哭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但你之前说过啊 大家都才认识的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.78,0:08:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们那时确实才认识不久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么时候变成挚友了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我还在北海道的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.72,0:08:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被我说中了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:08:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:08:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就你们三个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瞒着我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.03,0:09:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总之 我们从没有瞒着你做过什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你疑心病真重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.63,0:09:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像只有一件事没告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是我们四个确实是朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从什么时候开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么时候…不知不觉中？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所谓朋友就是这么回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是从没有人跟我说想当朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天也好好加油吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么时候开始变成朋友啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.23,0:09:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她肯定一直等人跟她说想当朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我们来跟她说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.82,0:10:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.44,0:10:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样简直像我逼你们说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别演了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谁知道呢 她说包在她身上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.18,0:10:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但她胆小和胆大的一面都挺极端的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安全帽戴了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安全帽戴了
