Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:31.96,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康中特圆体\bord6\fs45\b0\1c&H7E62B6&\3c&HE4E3D8&\pos(512,140)}午餐菜单{\i1}！{\i0}
