Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}绳子绑紧了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}绳子绑紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.47,0:10:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}脸色正常吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.58,0:10:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}脸色正常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}靴子穿好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.85,0:10:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}靴子穿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.04,0:10:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天一天也好好加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.85,0:10:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}注意安全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.83,0:10:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}注意安全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.52,0:10:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说好的室内工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里比室外还冷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鼻子都冻红了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都说要省电了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}室内工作动作要快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这些就是全部了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.58,0:10:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下来麻烦你们处理这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:10:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鸡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:10:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为是圣诞节啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们找个暖和的地方 帮它解冻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然我昨天开始就准备了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但感觉还不太够
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}暖和的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就拜托你们啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后你们两个就留在这里帮我的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那边肯定最好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管怎么看都太危险了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.02,0:11:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就给太阳晒晒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想 反正是永昼 太阳不会落下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.55,0:11:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这也是鸟肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们该吃还是会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且还有企鹅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.07,0:11:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}连鸡肉都不放过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我哪知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.37,0:11:41.40,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn@华康中特圆体\b0\bord0\1c&H555C5D&\frz275.6\pos(484,238)}敢碰就让你下地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.92,0:11:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}话说你那边没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.40,0:11:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 完美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天的点心完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是豪华
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难得的圣诞节嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有这么重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们知道基地生活中什么最重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吃饭和节日活动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}毕竟每天都在有限的区域内过单调的生活嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}点心时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.98,0:12:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}圣诞节蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.74,0:12:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不喜欢圣诞节吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}倒也说不上讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.12,0:12:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要说的话就跟庆祝生日一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很不公平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明每个人都有生日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有人能得到他人的祝贺 有人却不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的歌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}外面要先拍吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对啊 说是风势变强就可能会禁止外出了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.91,0:13:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}关于之前的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.78,0:13:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我决定要参演电视剧了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 我考虑了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肯定有不少人期待我出演吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我想拜托各位一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.30,0:13:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个 能请你们签字吗
