Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即使这趟旅行结束 很多时候不在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也能心安了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.52,0:13:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这种东西没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我以前都是一个人 所以我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.27,0:13:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算做这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.86,0:13:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.66,0:14:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你肯定不能理解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你肯定不能理解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不准吃剩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有本事吃剩 就别给我上厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有点冰块
