Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.56,0:14:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}结月要再来一碗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.65,0:14:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吃完饭后 我想和你说几句话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思 我正好有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.45,0:15:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我没有信心跟她说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难道放着不管吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可没这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.82,0:15:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小结
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别担心 她可没有生你的气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.24,0:15:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是小理都哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.51,0:15:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她只是有点寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.69,0:15:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别踢皮球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我做了什么怪事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实…也不是什么怪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果我站在你的立场上 我也会那么想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.10,0:15:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我觉得朋友不是嘴上说说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.15,0:15:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我经常听人这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.98,0:15:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那朋友究竟是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我说你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.46,0:15:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以说是种…感觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比方说小结喜欢小理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.49,0:16:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理听过就表示口说无凭 立字为据
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也不情愿吧 就像被怀疑了似的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.17,0:16:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请再给我盛一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.35,0:16:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这可能就是小理哭的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对小理来说 小结已经是她的朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我们是怎么成为朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么做才能交朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.24,0:16:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大概捕捉不到也无法形容吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}朋友与父母子女夫妻不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是种模糊的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.53,0:16:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算有天分开了 也没有人需要负责
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.32,0:16:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}至少对我而言是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但也正因这样才自由 朋友才能走到一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回来了
