Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}几乎没怎么回你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我就是能猜到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看着屏幕闪出的已读标记
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.25,0:18:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看她回复了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有时秒回 有时会隔点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有时半天后才回
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每次看到这些 我就能猜到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:56.32,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}そっと「会いたい」闻いた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.01,0:19:04.61,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}空に溶けて消えた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.48,0:19:22.38,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}今も胸の奥　静かに揺れている
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.38,0:19:29.97,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}白く辉く世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:38.52,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}残した足迹も消えて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:46.50,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}果てないと思ってた时が
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.98,0:19:54.77,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}终わりを告げる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:20:04.57,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}だからずっと忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:14.01,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}言叶より大切な思いが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.01,0:20:23.27,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}きっと繋いでくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:35.32,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}いつの日か　また旅に出よう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.55,0:20:46.17,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}だからずっと忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.36,0:20:55.81,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}一绪にいた　かけがえのない时が
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:21:04.94,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}きっと繋いでくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.07,0:21:15.09,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}いつまでも　いつまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:20.39,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}またね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:56.32,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}听见一声轻轻的「想见你」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.01,0:19:04.61,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}声音渐渐消失在了空中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.48,0:19:22.38,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}我的心底依然在暗自动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.38,0:19:29.97,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}雪白闪耀的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:38.52,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}我们踩下的足迹 渐渐褪去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:46.50,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}原以为这些时光 永无止境
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.98,0:19:54.77,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}却突然画上了句号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:20:04.57,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}所以这份心情 我不会忘怀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:14.01,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}它比任何语言 都要宝贵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.01,0:20:23.27,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}总有一天 会再度牵起你我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:35.32,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}带着我们 又一次踏上旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.55,0:20:46.17,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}所以这些时光 我不会忘怀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.36,0:20:55.81,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}你我一道 度过的珍贵点滴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:21:04.94,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}想必它们 会永远牵起你我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.07,0:21:15.09,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}直到永远 直到永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:20.39,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「现在在上课啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「在睡觉啦」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.22,0:18:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「在考虑要不要回复吧」之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.31,0:19:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我能猜到她是什么表情 很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对我而言 朋友大概就是这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.69,0:19:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然我也不怎么清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但大概就是这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起 可能帮不上你什么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.00,0:19:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}AND
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生日快乐！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}结月 你生日之前刚过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但那时我们一直在晕船 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以小理提议在南极帮你过生日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还请弓子小姐分了我们一些材料
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.67,0:19:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没做好的部分 就麻烦你用想象弥补啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.05,0:19:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}结月 生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.16,0:19:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快吹蜡烛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.75,0:20:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}刚见面时也是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人家才没哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不赶快吹就要融化了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}结月～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.68,0:20:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为…这是第一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.08,0:20:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有朋友帮我庆生…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.68,0:20:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快吹吧 结月
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人家的第一次啊…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.99,0:21:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}点心时间到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.14,0:21:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
